Postcard,on,the,Run,is,an,application,that,allows,users,to,take,photographs,personalize,them,with,messages,and,send,them,as,print,postcards,to,physical,mailing,addresses,The,Postcard,on,the,Run,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,Postcard,on,the,Run,functionality,into,other,applications,The,API,is,currently,in,private,beta,mode,and,they,are,accepting,requests,via,email,at,api,postcardontherun,com,Public,documentation,is,not,available,at,this,time